[I] A bunch of lints to catch common mistakes and improve Rust code

[T] A collection of lints to catch common mistakes and improve your Rust code.
[T]
[T] Lints are divided into categories, each with a default lint level. You can
[T] choose how much Clippy is supposed to annoy help you by changing the lint
[T] level by category.

[U] https://rust-lang.github.io/rust-clippy/

